---
title: Penne Primavera with Peas, Baby Spinach, and Creamy Ricotta
description: Here’s a recipe to celebrate the arrival of spring and its bounty of tender, sweet vegetables. It features a power lineup of baby spinach, peas, and fresh mint that fills the plate with a garden’s worth of green. The trio is tossed into al dente penne pasta and coated in a rich sauce that has both Parmesan and ricotta cheeses. If you love dishes that are wholesome and produce-heavy but with a comforting twist, this one is sure to be right up your alley.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/penne-primavera-c6c7c054.jpg
